# Directions to L100 Deikhan Aegis Trainer (High Priest, mob 6764)

say { "Hello";
	say Hello %n, the pleasure is mine.;
	say What can I do for you?;
	}

say { "Next trainer";
	tell %n Yes I can help you there..;
	tell %n But only a hint will I give you..;
	tell %n In the dim corridors where the winds howl,;
	tell %n past Pantathia's stone gates...;
	tell %n where the jungle is now...;
	tell %n there a guard must you bold;
	tell %n to enter and its shadowy folds.;
	}

